    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof and trunk. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits visible wear on the driver's seat bolster and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it remains sound and starts up without issue, though it may require some routine maintenance items in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
