    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated engineering. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring a seamless driving experience for the discerning motorist. Its robust performance profile and refined interior appointments make it an exceptional acquisition for those who demand both value and prestige. Viewings are available by appointment for qualified buyers.",
